IN RE Resignation of CHUPARKOFF 2018-1135 Supreme Court of Ohio. December 4, 2018

DISCIPLINARY CASE

Sua sponte, Mark Andrew Chuparkoff, Attorney Registration No. 0071982, last known business address in Akron, Ohio, found in contempt for failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before October 22, 2018.
